MENTORING

We offer mentoring for new golang/mgmt hackers who want to get involved. This is
fun and friendly! You get to improve your skills, and we get some patches in
return. Ping me off-list for details.


AI/LLM

It is permitted to use AI/LLM tooling to assist in bug finding and patch writing
but submitting unreviewed "slop" will get you banned. If anything, the new
tooling should make it possible to set a higher bar for quality. Please ensure
you meet and exceed that bar if you contribute to this project. The main author
has been able to achieve some big wins using this tooling. Your mileage may
vary. If you do use such tooling, its use must be disclosed in the commit
message. This is not to say that there aren't problematic aspects of this
tooling. At least for the moment, we believe the benefits to open source
outweigh the negatives. For more on this topic please read this post by the main
author: https://purpleidea.com/blog/2026/06/24/perspectives-on-ai-llms/


